OL,3,CResidents in over 55s block shocked at
OL,4,C100% increase for heating bills
OL,6,FIn a statement they've said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand and empathise with the
OL,8,Fconcerns of our customers at Wyvern
OL,9,FHouse, and of course apologise for any
OL,10,Fupset this has caused.J"Due to a long-
OL,11,Fterm fixed tariff we had in place, we
OL,12,Fhad been able to keep energy costs for
OL,13,Fthese customers lower in recent years
OL,14,F- the lowest contracted price in the
OL,15,Fcountry - while bills across the
OL,16,Fcountry rose exponentially.
