OL,6,F"That tariff expired in October, so
OL,7,Frises this year were inevitable as we
OL,8,Fmove more in line with current prices.
OL,9,F"When we set budgets for utility
OL,10,Fcharges, we have to estimate the usage
OL,11,Fbased on the data available at the
OL,12,Ftime.
