OL,3,CResidents in over 55s block shocked at
OL,4,C100% increase for heating bills
OL,6,F"However, we always review this
OL,7,Festimated charge once we have the full
OL,8,Fpicture, and this planned review has
OL,9,Fenabled us to recalculate the
OL,10,Festimates across this communal scheme
OL,11,Fand others, and for customers at
OL,12,FWyvern House, it will mean charges
OL,13,Flowering significantly from their
OL,14,Fcurrent rate.J"We'll contact customers
OL,15,Fdirectly to advise what the change is
OL,16,Ffor them in the coming days.
